  "body": "### Description\r\nAs an user, I want ``--engine-hostallowlist`` to screen incoming requests by the host or IP they're transmitted from, not the host they're intended to.\r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce (Bug)\r\n1. Set ``--engine-hostallowlist``\r\n2. Watch besu screen by the http ``Host`` header, instead of the actual incoming request's IP/hostname.\r\n3. Status ``403``\r\n\r\n**Expected behavior:** As described above\r\n\r\n**Actual behavior:** ``Forbidden 403``\r\n\r\n**Frequency:** 100%\r\n\r\n### Versions (Add all that apply)\r\n* Software version: 22.7.1\r\n",
